5^y = 81.
Add both equations.
3^x + 5^y = 125 + 81
3^x + 5^y = 5³ + 3⁴
By comparison, 
x = 4 ; y = 3.
xy = 4 × 3 = 12. Simple

3^x=125=5^3
Or 3=5^(3/x)

Now 5^y=81=3^4
Or 5^y={(5^(3/x))}4
Or 5^y=5^(12/x)
Or 5^xy=5^12
==>>xy=12
